						               													<description>Villages: Crystal Quest is the 7th expansion for the Villages card game&amp;ndash;and it&amp;rsquo;s the biggest one yet, with a monster-infested dungeon to explore and alternate rules that bring new life to all your existing cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In addition to waging war on other players, you can send your entire village to explore the dungeon and fight monsters as a group. Unit abilities interact with each other in new ways and each battle becomes a puzzle as you decide which monster each character should fight in order to defeat them all.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;For each monster destroyed, you&amp;rsquo;ll draw treasure cards, which give you extra gold at the end of the game. But what you&amp;rsquo;re really searching for are the Crystals&amp;ndash;six powerful gems, one in each color. The round will only end after a certain number of these have been discovered, allowing you to spend a little longer developing strategies and building your civilization before moving on to the next one.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Villages: Crystal Quest is an expansion that requires the Villages base game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Contains 69 cards and a rule booklet.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from publisher's website&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
